  * Modify d/watch and Source field in d/copyright to use HTTPS
  * Declare compliance with Debian policy 4.1.1
  * Use salsa.debian.org URLs in Vcs-{Browser,Git} fields

  [ Clint Adams ]
  * Bump to Standards-Version 4.1.4.

